{
  "chapter": 22,
  "chapter_summary": "第二十二回\"奇幻身法\"中，小弟带领黑杀组织成员进入城市，展示了果断狠辣的行事风格。扶桑浪人江岛和佐佐木在城中作恶，被武当叛徒白木制止。黑杀组织成员丁二郎和青蛇联手击杀了米家双剑。斧头赶来报告老柴与镖师冲突，但白木冷酷地决定放弃救援。土和尚在城中行凶，却神秘地被吊死在树上，连禅杖也不见踪影。大老板在公馆接见黑杀众人，竹叶青奉承众人。白木自信满满，认为七人足以对付阿吉。然而大老板展示出土和尚的禅杖，揭示了神秘高手的存在。少奶奶突然现身，展现出惊人的武功，连续击杀江岛和佐佐木。白木发现门外有高手，但大老板否认。整个章节展现了黑杀组织的冷酷无情和神秘高手的深不可测。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_di",
      "speaker_name": "小弟",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "活人的血是咸的，死人的血就咸的发苦。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 7,
      "line_end": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gui_gui",
      "speaker_name": "黑鬼",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我并没有问你这么多。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 9,
      "line_end": 9
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_di",
      "speaker_name": "小弟",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "要做一件事，就要做得确实地道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 11,
      "line_end": 11
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gui_gui",
      "speaker_name": "黑鬼",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这话是谁说的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 13,
      "line_end": 13
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_di",
      "speaker_name": "小弟",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "大老板说的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 15,
      "line_end": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gui_gui",
      "speaker_name": "黑鬼",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好，能够为他这种人做事，我们这趟来得就不算冤枉了。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 17,
      "line_end": 17
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_di",
      "speaker_name": "小弟",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那么就请随我来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 19,
      "line_end": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zuo_zuo_mu",
      "speaker_name": "佐佐木",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "花姑娘大大的漂亮。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 47,
      "line_end": 47
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_dao",
      "speaker_name": "江岛",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "大大的好。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 49,
      "line_end": 49
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zuo_zuo_mu",
      "speaker_name": "佐佐木",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "花姑娘不怕，我喜欢花姑娘。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 59,
      "line_end": 59
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_dao",
      "speaker_name": "江岛",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "花姑娘是我的，你……",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 63,
      "line_end": 63
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_mu",
      "speaker_name": "白木",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "要找花姑娘，到韩大奶奶那里去，有孩子的女人不是花姑娘。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 83,
      "line_end": 83
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "米家兄弟",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这道士想必就是被人从武当山赶下来的白木了，想不到现在还是这样的威风。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 87,
      "line_end": 87
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "米家兄弟",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "在自己人面前不发威，你叫他到哪里发威去？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 89,
      "line_end": 89
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_mu",
      "speaker_name": "白木",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "看来这地方倒真热闹得很，居然连米家兄弟也到了。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 91,
      "line_end": 91
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "米家兄弟",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这老杂毛好灵的耳朵。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 93,
      "line_end": 93
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_er_lang",
      "speaker_name": "丁二郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "原来米家双剑也不过如此，我们一直钉在他们后面，他们竟像死人一样，完全不知道。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 111
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_she",
      "speaker_name": "青蛇",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "所以现在他们才会真的变成死人。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 113,
      "line_end": 113
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_mu",
      "speaker_name": "白木",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "青蛇轻功一向是好的，想不到二郎的轻功也有精进。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 115,
      "line_end": 115
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_er_lang",
      "speaker_name": "丁二郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那只因为我暂时还不想死。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 117,
      "line_end": 117
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_mu",
      "speaker_name": "白木",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好，说得好，这件事办得也好！",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 123
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_er_lang",
      "speaker_name": "丁二郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "最好的是什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_mu",
      "speaker_name": "白木",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "最好的当然还是我这把剑。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 129,
      "line_end": 129
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_she",
      "speaker_name": "青蛇",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不知道斧头又闯了什么祸。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 141,
      "line_end": 141
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_mu",
      "speaker_name": "白木",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "闯祸的只怕不是他。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 143,
      "line_end": 143
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_tou",
      "speaker_name": "斧头",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我总算赶上你们了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 145,
      "line_end": 145
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_mu",
      "speaker_name": "白木",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "什么事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 147,
      "line_end": 147
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_tou",
      "speaker_name": "斧头",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "老柴又喝醉了酒，在城外和一批河北道上镖师干了起来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 149,
      "line_end": 149
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_mu",
      "speaker_name": "白木",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "闯祸的果然又是他。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_tou",
      "speaker_name": "斧头",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我看见的时候，他已经挨了两下子，想不到连我加上去都不行，只好杀开一条血路闯出来找救兵。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 155,
      "line_end": 155
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_mu",
      "speaker_name": "白木",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哼！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 157,
      "line_end": 157
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_tou",
      "speaker_name": "斧头",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那批镖师实在扎手得很，大家再不赶去，老柴只怕就死定了。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 159,
      "line_end": 159
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_mu",
      "speaker_name": "白木",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那么就让他去死吧！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 161,
      "line_end": 161
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_tou",
      "speaker_name": "斧头",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "让他去死？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 163,
      "line_end": 163
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_mu",
      "speaker_name": "白木",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我们这次是来杀人的，不是来被杀的！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 165,
      "line_end": 165
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "据说各位一进城，就做了几件惊人的事，真是好极了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 229
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_mu",
      "speaker_name": "白木",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "一点都不好。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 231,
      "line_end": 231
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "可是现在城里的人，已没有一个不知道各位的厉害了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 233,
      "line_end": 233
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_tou",
      "speaker_name": "斧头",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "气死我了！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 239,
      "line_end": 239
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "斧头兄为何生气？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 241,
      "line_end": 241
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_tou",
      "speaker_name": "斧头",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我自己喜欢生气，一高兴就要生气！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 243,
      "line_end": 243
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那更好极了！",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_tou",
      "speaker_name": "斧头",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那有什么好？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 249,
      "line_end": 249
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "就凭阁下这一股怒气，就足以令人心寒胆破！",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 251,
      "line_end": 251
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_er_lang",
      "speaker_name": "丁二郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "可是我就从来不生气！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 253,
      "line_end": 253
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那也好！",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 255,
      "line_end": 255
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_er_lang",
      "speaker_name": "丁二郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "有什么好？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 257,
      "line_end": 257
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "平时静如处子，动时必如脱免，平时若是不发，发必定惊人。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 259,
      "line_end": 259
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_er_lang",
      "speaker_name": "丁二郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "看来不管我们怎么说，你总有法子称赞我们几句，这倒也是本事。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 261,
      "line_end": 261
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "在下既没有各位这样的功夫，就只有靠这点本事混混饭吃。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 265
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "speaker_name": "大老板",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "各位的人已到齐了么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 269
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_mu",
      "speaker_name": "白木",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "到齐了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 271,
      "line_end": 271
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "speaker_name": "大老板",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我却记得这次来的好像应该是九位。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 273,
      "line_end": 273
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_mu",
      "speaker_name": "白木",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "嗯。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 275,
      "line_end": 275
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "speaker_name": "大老板",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "还有两位呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 277,
      "line_end": 277
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_mu",
      "speaker_name": "白木",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那两个人来不来都一样。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 279,
      "line_end": 279
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "speaker_name": "大老板",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 281,
      "line_end": 281
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_mu",
      "speaker_name": "白木",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "有我们七个人来了，无论做什么都已足够。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 283,
      "line_end": 283
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "speaker_name": "大老板",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "对付阿吉也已足够？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 285,
      "line_end": 285
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_mu",
      "speaker_name": "白木",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不管对付什么人都已足够。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 287,
      "line_end": 287
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "speaker_name": "大老板",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我知道近来道长的剑术又有精进，其余的几位也都是好手，只不过有件事却总是让我放心不下。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 289,
      "line_end": 289
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_mu",
      "speaker_name": "白木",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "什么事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 291,
      "line_end": 291
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "speaker_name": "大老板",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "各位想必是认得这根禅杖的！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 297,
      "line_end": 297
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "speaker_name": "大老板",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "据说这根禅杖一向和土和尚寸步不离，却不知怎会到了别人手里？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 301,
      "line_end": 301
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_mu",
      "speaker_name": "白木",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "贫道正想请教，这根禅杖是从哪里来的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 303,
      "line_end": 303
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "speaker_name": "大老板",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "有个人特地送来，要我转交给各位。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 305,
      "line_end": 305
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_mu",
      "speaker_name": "白木",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他的人还在不在？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 307,
      "line_end": 307
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "speaker_name": "大老板",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "还在。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 309,
      "line_end": 309
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_mu",
      "speaker_name": "白木",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "在哪里？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 311,
      "line_end": 311
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "speaker_name": "大老板",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "就在那里。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 313,
      "line_end": 313
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zuo_zuo_mu",
      "speaker_name": "佐佐木",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这花姑娘果然不是花姑娘，是个女妖怪。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 330,
      "line_end": 331
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_nai_nai",
      "speaker_name": "少奶奶",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你喜不喜欢女妖怪？",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 333,
      "line_end": 333
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_mu",
      "speaker_name": "白木",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小心。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 339,
      "line_end": 339
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "speaker_name": "大老板",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这就是你特地请来保护我的？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 353,
      "line_end": 353
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "speaker_name": "大老板",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "凭他们就能够对付阿吉？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 359,
      "line_end": 359
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "speaker_name": "大老板",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我看他们连一个女人都对付不了，怎么能……",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 363,
      "line_end": 363
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_mu",
      "speaker_name": "白木",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "朋友既然来了，为何躲在门外，不敢露面？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 366,
      "line_end": 367
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "speaker_name": "大老板",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你是在跟谁说话？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 369,
      "line_end": 369
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_mu",
      "speaker_name": "白木",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "门外的那位朋友。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 371,
      "line_end": 371
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "speaker_name": "大老板",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "门外有你的朋友？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 373,
      "line_end": 373
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "speaker_name": "大老板",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "绝没有，我可以保证绝对没有。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 375,
      "line_end": 375
    }
